<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for signing up. Your account is now active, and you can start using our services immediately.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us anytime.</p>

        <a href="#" class="btn">Visit Dashboard</a>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>